{"tid":430014,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺 Pacific Rim 部主角機 design 得好迤?","createTime":"2017-10-09T12:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T11:10:42.000Z","uid":37125,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0c08e414936eadb1d5d41625dc92d650d3c55b","tid":430014,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"其實咁多人鍾意依套戲嘅原因只係啲 CG 同 soundtrack 做得好. 當佢 close up 嗰時見到啲 mechanic layer 喺度郁來郁去, 聽到啲機械聲嗰時咪正囉. 當你部機械人冇晒啲電影鏡頭,  CG layer, soundtrack 去襯托的話, 部機械人就會係噉嘅樣:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.thinkgeek.com/images/products/zoom/13e9_18_in_gipsy_danger_battle.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkgeek.com%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fzoom%2F13e9_18_in_gipsy_danger_battle.jpg&h=04fde56a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吸唔吸引? 加埋戰損 effect 畀你, 想唔想買翻隻係屋企擺? 超級系同現實系各有自己嘅味道, 依隻嘢迤唔關口味問題. 佢迤嘅程度同新 Power Ranger 部 &quot;機械人&quot; 有得比. 以為亂鳩咁加 details 就得? 一部機械人有冇放過心機落去 design 係睇得出, 最迤係佢個頭.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hdwallpapers.in/walls/pacific_rim-wide.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hdwallpapers.in%2Fwalls%2Fpacific_rim-wide.jpg&h=081ae585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只係覺得好可惜, 如果  Pacific Rim 啲機械人有放過心機落去 design 嘅話, 依套嘢唔只去到依個級數. (純Popcorn片嚟講)<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 啲配角機反而仲好過部主角機, 至少有翻啲 character, 冇咁路人卒仔 feel."},{"pid":"fbfe919d528f0d214cca6ce43001ef64c96e6fb2","tid":430014,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"ramin djawadi 出親既soundtrack 都好好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91e0181f05797a04543da7a57d45cf8ccbb0b8f","tid":430014,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T13:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eee5a95f5250ae26b9a2407bdb66bc8aae825e8","tid":430014,"uid":2386,"l